    <decisions>
        <description>Send pharmacy consultation need to notification path. For a CT case with follow up fields filled out, and status of Open, Closed, or Opened in Error, make a follow up scheduling case.</description>
        <name>Send_Notifications</name>
        <label>Send Notifications</label>
        <locationX>578</locationX>
        <locationY>134</locationY>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Notify_Pharmacist</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>caseRecord.VCC_Pharmacy_Consultation_Needed__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>true</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Get_Custom_Notification_ID</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Notify Pharmacist</label>
        </rules>
        <rules>
            <name>Create_Follow_up_Case</name>
            <conditionLogic>1 AND 2 AND (3 OR 4 OR 5)</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>caseRecord.RecordType.DeveloperName</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>VCC_Clinical_Triage</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>caseRecord.VCC_Follow_Up_Appt_Needed__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>NotEqualTo</operator>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>caseRecord.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>Contains</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Closed</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>caseRecord.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Opened in Error</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>caseRecord.Status</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Open</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Get_Admin_Record_TypeID</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Create Follow up Case</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>A subflow that is called by VCC Case Flow - After Upsert to send the pharmacy follow up appointment and create a new follow up appointment case that is placed in the MSA queue.
PS 1.20.0 - Added more filter criteria to &apos;update existing scheduling case record&apos;
1.20.1 - Added logic to create MSA follow up case even if original caseRecord Status is open (and follow up fields are not blank)</description>
